Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mizuki Himeji is diligent{\i0}\N{\i1}in everything she does.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like today, when she is{\i0}\N{\i1}researching on an unfamiliar topic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"How to deliver a love letter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:31.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As expected, it's best to give it in person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll convey your feelings better{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}--and will increase the possibility{\i0}\N{\i1}of getting a good response."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,--Himeji! Are you studying?\N{\i1}--and will increase the possibility of getting a good response."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Throb Counter"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. I was just researching something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah! If I boldly give it to him now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Y... Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:54.26,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth... This... is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,P... Please don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! That wasn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is this funny?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hottoite sodatsu mono nanda nandarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one more{\i0}\N{\i1}chance. Never never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance. Never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deai mashite wa kantan sugiruyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saisho ni kimeta kotae wa hitotsu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokimeki mashita goukaku shimasuka?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koi mo shoubu mo awatenai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotsu kotsu kotsu to tetsuya ni tameiki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watashi no naka ni tensai dreamer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Omou koto mina kanaeba iina{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hito no sekai wa kinishinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zettai koko de matterunda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area nozomu koe ga kikoeruyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Ear! Ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Tomaranai surechigai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watashi ga soudan aite nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Tomodachi kai?" "Tomodachi desu."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanashiki rei ten dane{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Yarinaoshi kakinaoshi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honki de one more chance please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ima yori suteki na mirai ga arunoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ima yori suteki ni my life, my life, my life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:39.95,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10" "Prep Tests, Mysterious Thieves, and Love Letters"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:43.29,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10" "Prep Tests, Mysterious Thieves, and Love Letters"\N{\i1}Akihisa Yoshii. Year 2, Class F.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.16,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10" "Prep Tests, Mysterious Thieves, and Love Letters"\N{\i1}It's another typical morning for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up please, Aki! It's morning already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'm still sleepy.\N--It can't be helped, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a "good\Nmorning" kiss to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm up! I'm up, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a "have a\Ngood day" kiss in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want it in advance or on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh well... Then I'll stop\Nwith the family bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and change. Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Breakfast? But you can't cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,"CalorieMaido"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I knew it'd be something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a nutritiously-balanced supplement food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Since there isn't much time to spare in\Nthe morning, I prepared the drink type.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really feel\Nlike I'm having breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's nutritious so that's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Taking in enough calories in the\Nmorning, when your day is just starting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,and having a light meal at night,\Nwhen you become less active, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...good for your health, they say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:45.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Assuming that you take in\Nabout 2500 calories a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be appropriate to allocate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,1000 calories to breakfast and\Nlunch, and 500 calories to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,This one can is 200 calories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So please drink 5 cans, 1 liter, for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I can't drink that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,If you drink 13 cans, which is 2.6 liters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,the numbers match up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I can't drink that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just so you won't get\Ntired of them, I prepared different kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The main is "normal" flavor,\Nthe side dish is "corn soup" flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The drink is "coffee" flavor, and for dessert,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,please choose the one you'd like,\Neither "café au lait" flavor or "cocoa" flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not really the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. I'm sorry. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you're at a growing\Nstage, this isn't enough, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't add more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa's happy morning{\i0}\N{\i1}is still far in the distance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ugh"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish she had at least\Ncombined them with the solid kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Taking routine measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Measurements?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm recording the stats on\Nbust sizes in this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.17,Main,,0,0,0,,A 10 cm difference between full-\Nand under-bust measurements is A cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,After that, each 2.5 cm\Nincrease becomes B, C, D cups...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,B, C, A... A, B, D, B, B, C...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,B, A... Ah! That's over G! D, A, B, A...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that a D?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... I'm impressed that you could tell that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? This is quite small. Is this A cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No. After A cup, each 2.5 cm decrease\Nin the full- and under-bust difference
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.78,Main,,0,0,0,,becomes AA, AAA...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Then if it's flat like the one\Nwe just saw, that'd be five As, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,just like a {\i1}shachihoko{\i0}, my\Nspine is bent! Broken! Curved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Even those with flat chests have human rights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I give! I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahh! My eyes! My eyes!\N--You can't watch that, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,A little more... A little more...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Not the Rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys are lively, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.69,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hideyoshi? Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it! You're gonna comfort me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Male Nurse"\N"Comfort"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a costume for the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a costume\Nfor a male nurse, but when I wear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,it looks like it was made for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That should be "nurse," not "male nurse."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Then I misread the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No wonder the front of\Nthe underwear doesn't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.17,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Rumble, rumble, rumble, rumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.34,Main,,0,0,0,,The top was the type\Nthat opens in front, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, what're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,If you act stupid, people\Nwill look at me the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not acting stupid, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Not realizing it yourself\Nproves that you're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You being in Class F alone is bad enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,but on top of that, it's a parade of idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed just to be a\Nstudent in the same academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What can I say? It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:02.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, has your class's academic\Nperformance gotten better since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,If you have time to fool around,\NI want you to study. Let's go, Rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"Humiliation"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Around that time, Mizuki Himeji{\i0}\N{\i1}was reading a specialized book.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.02,Main,,0,0,0,,"How to deliver a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,When you don't have\Ncourage to give it in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,you can ask a close friend as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,A close... friend... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,About Yoshii... To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that... Could it be that you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Is it possible that... you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have ones that I'm missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've asked Yoshii's\Nclose friend, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a big favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth... it's a love letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Shouko! I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You're already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,A marriage registration form?! Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never sign i--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,How mortifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"If it's hard to give just the love letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,you can also give a present along with it."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth... there's\Nsomething I'd like to give to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I baked cookies this mornin--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...? Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Where are you?! Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.32,Main,,0,0,0,,--Please have the cookies that I baked!\N--I was here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,--Please have the cookies that I baked!\N--Shh! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If she finds us, both of our lives will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you fooling around for, Yoshii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Iron Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Good timing! Help me carry some stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"You can also secretly put\Nit in their bag or shoe locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That seems modest and sometimes\Nit helps increase your likeability."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've done this from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,"Throb Counter"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah... U-Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Th--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.19,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Busty Pudding" "Get off with Pudding" "Loads of sexy photos of\Nthe busty, ponytailed Pudding!" "Expanded Issue" "Afro Publishing"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If Shouko gets her hands on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,my life will be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's finally completed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,The Complete Statistics on\NBust Sizes! No copying is allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,In the end... I couldn't even\Nput it in his shoe locker, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! This envelope is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,This is rare in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, no! Where's my love letter?\NDid I drop it somewhere earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:10.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Man... Why am I the only one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Feedback!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,C... Could it be... the\Nquestions for the next exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means if I see these...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If I know the questions in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,even I could get a 100% score!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. That would be cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,If I suddenly get a 100% score,\Npeople will suspect me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The box is torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll use the cardboard boxes\Nfrom my classroom or something instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,"Enough with the stupidity --Principal"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Humph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll see them again when you take\Nthe prep test. Start preparing for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! There it is! Good! I found i--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Delivery... slip?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:09.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What...? Whaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Himeji?\NYou look bummed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it? If there's something\NI can do to help, just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go? My marriage registration form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,The bust size list that\NI worked my ass off to complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,My treasured pictures that\NI went out of my way to buy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did my costume go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! I put it in\Nthe safe and securely locked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about the cardboard\Nboxes, Iron Man took some earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,--Wh...\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,--And...\N--Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,An important envelope was...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So don't you have some idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... at the place I dropped it, I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The delivery slip for the\Nprep test exam papers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Then... when I dropped the exam\Npapers... it got mixed into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,That safe is locked and students are not\Nsupposed to open it without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a stranger! Just ask us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We can depend on each\Nother when we have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That safe has things that\Nare important to us as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.88,Main,,0,0,0,,They may not be worth anything to others, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,They have our feelings in them!\NThey're important to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll take them back no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone... Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's join hands and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their feelings were not together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.89,Main,,0,0,0,,So they're in this safe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a double lock that requires the\Nkey and the secret code number to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,So it won't open with just the\Nkey or just the code number, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What tight security.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just have\NAki's Avatar break the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one who gets scolded, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Our drama club once performed\Na story about a mysterious thief,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,and the thief used some technique\Nto steal a treasure from a safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,How did he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,First, he prepared a fake treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Then he showed the fake treasure to\Nthe owner and told them that he stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The owner panicked and\Nopened the safe to check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, there, he stole the treasure for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That's smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That's an explanation\Neven idiots can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then! Let's use that strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Iron Man... Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the prep test exam paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, give that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... don't you have to\Nopen the safe and check?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Do I need to do that when you\Nhave it in your hand right now, Yoshii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But... Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It went well on stage, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to open it on our own after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,We need both the key and the secret code number.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What're we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:21.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kyouji Nemoto. He is{\i0}\N{\i1}the rep for Year 2, Class B.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is open that safe,\Nright? Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You can do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't do it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,but if you obtain the key,\NI'll handle the secret code number.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We can depend on each other\Nwhen we have problems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's the key to the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! It's right behind Mr. Nishimura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then! Let's go with a decoy strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.27,Main,,0,0,0,,A-A decoy strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone will use their\Nfemale charm to get his attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,and we'll take the key in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, Hideyoshi is perfect for that job, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Because we can't let Himeji do such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.40,Main,,0,0,0,,and since Minami doesn't have\Nany sexual charm, she'd mess up--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,My spine! My spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"Argentine Backbreaker"\N"Japanese Name: Argentine-Style Back Bend"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--Who'd you say doesn't have any sexual charm?!\N--I give! I give up! I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:14.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well... There're many reasons for this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,and we're doing nothing ba-- Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,First my backbone, and now my skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Man... That was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That went deep, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But in that opening, I got the key to the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yaay! Yaay!\N--Good job, Muttsulini. Just as we planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.22,Main,,0,0,0,,So I was the decoy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! It's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The next is the secret code number, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it carelessly. If we\Nmake a mistake, the alarm will go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you know it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,a nice digital camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is from earlier when\NIron Man opened the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's got pictures of him pressing the buttons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is the\Nsecret code number for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad... that I was able to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I found mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better keep it more secure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:14.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Really... thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I found it! My costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A... A bra, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that, it's a front-hook bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what it's like, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? Mizuki, you don't\Nknow about front-hook bras?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,They don't have it for my size. They\Nsaid that the cups are too big for the clasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true! The clasps are well made!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Who decided that front-hook\Nbras are for flat chests?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--Too big...\N--Was it the country? Mountains? Rivers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm, so this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Nemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, just a little preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Nemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:58.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying now?\NYou guys are the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You entered the safe where the exam\Npapers were kept without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,If they find that out,\Nyou guys are cheaters, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! We just came to get what we lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You think such an excuse would work, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Has your time in Class F caused\Nyou to get infected by their stupidity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Results are all that matters\Nin this world. In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,the means doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! But you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm able to solve\Nthese questions on the test day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,then it's my real ability, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The questions given on that day\Nhappen to be the same questions. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That logic is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to ruin this rare chance?\NThat's why you guys are idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,"Idiots"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if my scores improve a bit,\Nthere'll be no harm to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I live honestly,\Nthere'll be no benefit to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't even understand that,\Nand that's why you guys are in Class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not just your academic performance\Nthat's bad, it's your brains themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why it's the lowest class,\Nhome to all the academy's scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true that Class F's academic\Nperformance may not be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But... But everyone's kind... considerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,fun and warm... It's a very nice class!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:21.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Class F is neither the\Nlowest nor scum by any means!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Humph! Either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,if they find out about this,\Nyou'll be suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,or expelled in the worst case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You and I share the same fate. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you were doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And you didn't see me\Nhere, either. That's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Try and wise up, you dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Are we...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,idiots after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're just realizing it now?\NWe are genuine idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you upset that you were made a fool of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care if someone makes a fool of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:16.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But... when Himeji, Minami\Nand the others are bad-mouthed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji could've actually studied\Nin Class A's better environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She just happened to have bad\Nluck and became a Class F student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,When that's all it was, why does she\Nhave to be made a fool of like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph! If you're that upset, do you wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Three months have almost passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The period in which the losing class\Ncannot declare war is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I led the class to a loss because\NI took it lightly last time. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's also true that we got close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't make the same clumsy mistake ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:20:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,How about it, do you wanna try one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?! Of course, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll win this time and show\Neveryone we're no ordinary idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, the Summoner Test War!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Well then, let's\Ngo settle things, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go ask Himeji to give me her cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not fair that we're the only ones\Nwho get the short end of the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar. Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.98,MainTop,,0,0,0,,vs. "Combined Subjects"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the prep test exam paper... isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means that if I memorize this,\NI'll get a 100% score in the next test!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, they're real idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Questions that were made\Npublic won't be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Did Aki and Yuuji do this by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Sakamoto! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.11,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning... of doing such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,We were just trying to play a prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,We got too carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't lie! What're you up t--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We're really... sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason you can't tell me the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No. This was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you two... ever meekly apologized before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay... Then you're both\Ngetting the demon's remedial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Be prepared! I'll teach\Nyou even better than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a punishment for your prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-A-K-A Go Go Home!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:19.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-A-K-A Go Go Home!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jugyou owari shifuku no jikan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tatoeru no nara “Maji de Angel!”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fui no kokuchi heiwa kowashita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:32.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsuishi no shirase “Jigoku da!”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:35.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomodachi tono warai banashi ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}“Iru wake naiyo sonna baka”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demo hontou wa mune no oku dewa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakendetanda “Jibun ga! Sou deshita!”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chuusha jou de miru “Tsukigime” no koto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaisha no namae dato omotteta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:23:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zutto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baka mo tooseba otoko date{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bokura no joushiki hijoushiki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:09.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruuru wa muyou sa kono sekai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yakiniku teishoku gekokujou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nishi kara nobotta ohisama ga shizunde iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hashire! Mou gohan da{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ouchi ni kaerou! Ouchi ni kaerou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,"Nemoto"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's this? A present from a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm quite the guy, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'll eat them before Yuuka finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the sound of his soul being taken away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 11.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was the tactic often used by{\i0}\N{\i1}the German military during World War II{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that used a combination of{\i0}\N{\i1}bombing and armored divisions?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go full blast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please value your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next Episode! "Rivals,{\i0}\N{\i1}Love Letters, and Blitz Tactics."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be on the test.{\i0}
